{"tid":690610,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"風景如畫法羅群島","createTime":"2018-06-05T04:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T03:24:02.000Z","uid":172556,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0d767af058a029a5b84d2de04d5dbc239a70f7ba","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1h9lxkds\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1h9lxkds&h=7268aef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人在泰國無野做，介紹下上個月去過喺法國群島。<br />\n<br />\n法羅群島係一個位於冰島同北歐大陸之間嘅島國。<br />\n<br />\n齋講山山水水，法羅群島係我覺得自己去過最靚嘅歐洲國家，比挪威瑞士更加風光如畫。喺挪威瑞士，你都要搭車坐船去景點，但喺法羅群島，四方八面都好似一幅畫咁，每分每寸都係一個景點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pgroby04\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpgroby04&h=000dc0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dvkj27mt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdvkj27mt&h=d3ddb6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一眼望哂嘅第二大城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lmop12cd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flmop12cd&h=88cb33a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0fyn9wig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0fyn9wig&h=801bfda4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jh4fopv1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjh4fopv1&h=a92d0b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首都市中心內一間叫『柒』嘅中國餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7wxktbr3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7wxktbr3&h=1b4fa121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m64dwklb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm64dwklb&h=ab26a0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海邊嘅瀑布<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wkyvojpd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwkyvojpd&h=a5c0c733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q2kit0b9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq2kit0b9&h=c45219ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7iezs3fk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7iezs3fk&h=561a773a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j8ew19a4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj8ew19a4&h=7ba29b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法羅群島國旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f2pmjg79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff2pmjg79&h=3fd985c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHostel附近嘅小漁村。住宿方面，全法羅群島只有一間hostel，多數遊客住airbnb。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/chml984t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fchml984t&h=b0a62980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾意山山水水，而又唔想去冰島挪威同人迫嘅巴絲可以諗諗!"},{"pid":"24393f8fd3c4eaaf31c5aaa4f95e3f3cc150068c","tid":690610,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"冷門地方，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你邊度飛去？當地消費如何，同英國、瑞士比較的話？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有咩食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f055f7aea2d3fad220e3ca70397efede42b2266","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打揸車定搭巴士？<br />\n我呢個月尾去 啱啱開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c770430d94234e3558629cf356631a3007848f","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24393f8fd3c4eaaf31c5aaa4f95e3f3cc150068c","tid":690610,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"冷門地方，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你邊度飛去？當地消費如何，同英國、瑞士比較的話？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有咩食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"由哥本哈根飛去，淡季機票好平，來回好似300美金。<br />\n<br />\n食方面，依邊嘅人鍾意fast food，炸雞薯條fish and chips嗰類，最抵食就pizza，140hkd一個medium pizza。法羅群島出名三文魚，9x%收入來自捕魚，但喺嗰邊食三文魚係貴到仆街，一份煎三文魚300hkd。本地人會食鯨魚海鷗同puffin，但多數收埋自己食，出面無得賣。"},{"pid":"8dc172e948d17ad5fe4fc74cb6e311b3227715fe","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f055f7aea2d3fad220e3ca70397efede42b2266","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打揸車定搭巴士？<br />\n我呢個月尾去 啱啱開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"我無車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打一定要租車，係一!定!要!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n好多景點係無公共交通去，一係揸車一係hitch-hike。<br />\n<br />\n巴打去幾耐? 嗰邊天氣好癡線，好反常，如果想行山影靚景，預多少少時間等好天先去景點"},{"pid":"fb8a9a75f1d8c777c0d1f6fd58b0d4baf50b0663","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc172e948d17ad5fe4fc74cb6e311b3227715fe","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f055f7aea2d3fad220e3ca70397efede42b2266","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打揸車定搭巴士？<br />\n我呢個月尾去 啱啱開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"我無車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打一定要租車，係一!定!要!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n好多景點係無公共交通去，一係揸車一係hitch-hike。<br />\n<br />\n巴打去幾耐? 嗰邊天氣好癡線，好反常，如果想行山影靚景，預多少少時間等好天先去景點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"我都冇車牌呀 所以應該都要行下山或者單車<br />\n我去四日咋 希望天氣唔太差啦<br />\n聽講話天氣會變得好快？"},{"pid":"191e8ee21431a80455e8e2c92aa6b722f0872741","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb8a9a75f1d8c777c0d1f6fd58b0d4baf50b0663","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc172e948d17ad5fe4fc74cb6e311b3227715fe","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f055f7aea2d3fad220e3ca70397efede42b2266","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打揸車定搭巴士？<br />\n我呢個月尾去 啱啱開始plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"我無車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打一定要租車，係一!定!要!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n好多景點係無公共交通去，一係揸車一係hitch-hike。<br />\n<br />\n巴打去幾耐? 嗰邊天氣好癡線，好反常，如果想行山影靚景，預多少少時間等好天先去景點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"我都冇車牌呀 所以應該都要行下山或者單車<br />\n我去四日咋 希望天氣唔太差啦<br />\n聽講話天氣會變得好快？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有踩開單車? 因為嗰邊啲路全部上落斜，有心理準備上斜踩到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n係，依刻萬里無雲，好好太陽，半個鐘之後成天黑雲，再半個鐘就落狗屎加打風，有幾日我見到大風到吹郁燈柱，然後再過半個鐘無哂雲好好太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋巴打如果行山要小心啲，因為山上超大風，大風到會吹郁我(但我本身瘦底)，同埋山頂path又滑又斜，仲要成日好大霧，本地人教我，如果行山時突然大霧，一定唔好再行，坐定定等霧散先好繼續，否則好危險"},{"pid":"e12f7bf3ec7e930a6cd5a96d23052559e7067634","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"191e8ee21431a80455e8e2c92aa6b722f0872741","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb8a9a75f1d8c777c0d1f6fd58b0d4baf50b0663","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc172e948d17ad5fe4fc74cb6e311b3227715fe","tid":690610,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"我無車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打一定要租車，係一!定!要!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n好多景點係無公共交通去，一係揸車一係hitch-hike。<br />\n<br />\n巴打去幾耐? 嗰邊天氣好癡線，好反常，如果想行山影靚景，預多少少時間等好天先去景點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"我都冇車牌呀 所以應該都要行下山或者單車<br />\n我去四日咋 希望天氣唔太差啦<br />\n聽講話天氣會變得好快？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有踩開單車? 因為嗰邊啲路全部上落斜，有心理準備上斜踩到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n係，依刻萬里無雲，好好太陽，半個鐘之後成天黑雲，再半個鐘就落狗屎加打風，有幾日我見到大風到吹郁燈柱，然後再過半個鐘無哂雲好好太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋巴打如果行山要小心啲，因為山上超大風，大風到會吹郁我(但我本身瘦底)，同埋山頂path又滑又斜，仲要成日好大霧，本地人教我，如果行山時突然大霧，一定唔好再行，坐定定等霧散先好繼續，否則好危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"咁睇嚟要再諗過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你係自己去定有同伴<br />\n我諗緊一條友行山會唔會有危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36269d6b4deb06461c73b073b10a94b44a09c19","tid":690610,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"873c222b1d53f87731f595548a8cbef54435f50b","tid":690610,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"腳呀！ 奶呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad792b97c03f23a9f744befe116cbcbbbeace47","tid":690610,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"本身好撚想去法羅自駕遊<br />\n但知佢地殺🐳殺🐧黎食之後扣左少少分<br />\n利申：非左膠"},{"pid":"f742e1087dc8df04259a58183c58864bffe22332","tid":690610,"uid":153796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"依家喺法羅群島<br />\nplan咗幾個巴士去倒嘅地方"},{"pid":"f27e7d1a6a882a4bff17d675edaddbf9659507b7","tid":690610,"uid":153796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"巴打行咗咩山？<br />\n你有無行開山，我都少少驚危險"},{"pid":"06a92eed37daf9dc0c9180a76a5cbeced5589d09","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f742e1087dc8df04259a58183c58864bffe22332","tid":690610,"uid":153796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"依家喺法羅群島<br />\nplan咗幾個巴士去倒嘅地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"去咗邊幾個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58535f111062c74126a32cf8c87b6f31d25dce7b","tid":690610,"uid":36779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"巴打 有冇去mykines 睇puffin? <br />\n我之前去依度兩個禮拜， 日日行山咁制<br />\n全部山頭都無樹 真係勁正<br />\n但係d 山路 嚴格黎講唔叫路 得個指示牌比你 左邊係 山涯 右邊係loose stone 堆 都夠膽死比人行"},{"pid":"33b3264b6075fcfb266442f55915630fe9f8d8d7","tid":690610,"uid":36779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/195933_78e3e288d5a0f933c6fd73c857b78915.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F195933_78e3e288d5a0f933c6fd73c857b78915.png&h=34c23f19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f03a9f933f0364d6818f1843b966b1bd182dc7c","tid":690610,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"CHING好有錢 成日去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a8a87a0bf352b9da31a0b7ec38fb3322308b45","tid":690610,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"想見puffin 真身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdab8ea1658f7ff270c81f932b45c2cfd5c3add","tid":690610,"uid":153796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06a92eed37daf9dc0c9180a76a5cbeced5589d09","tid":690610,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f742e1087dc8df04259a58183c58864bffe22332","tid":690610,"uid":153796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"依家喺法羅群島<br />\nplan咗幾個巴士去倒嘅地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"去咗邊幾個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"